description: Linked to a terrible secret from the past, an accident in a government lab turns the nearby village inhabitants into creatures that seem impossible to kill. A small group of survivors must hold out for the night until a special rescue team can arrive and save them from these unstoppable monsters that have not only been made real, but also made to perfection.
